  <brief_title>Medial Cervical Block for Carotid Endarterectomy Comparison With Standard Method</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison of Medial Cervical Plexus Block Versus Combined (Superficial and Deep) Cervical Plexus Block for Carotid Endarterectomy: A Prospective, Randomized Single Blind Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
