  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to compare efficacy, complications and safety of the standard
      method of Combined (superficial and deep) cervical plexus block (SDCPB) with Ultrasound
      guided Medial Cervical plexus block technique (MCPB).

      Hypothesis: Ultrasound assisted MCPB is safer than SDCPB with similar efficacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
